subject: Re: [junit] is junit compliant with jdk1.5
msgSnippet: ... I believe it builds without problems on JDK 5.0. ... There s nothing to say: download it and build it from source. You should be fine. -- J. B. (Joe)
messageBody:
Rajeev R wrote:

> Does junit3.8 supports jdk 1.5.

I believe it builds without problems on JDK 5.0.

> Please tell me the details about this,since I am using jdk1.5
> in my project.

There's nothing to say: download it and build it from source. You should
be fine.
